'''SSBJ 'A' ''' is an under-17 [[football (soccer)|soccer]] team from [[Malaysia]] representing the [[Sekolah Sukan Bukit Jalil]]. The team's squad is made up of students of the [[Bukit Jalil Sports School]]. [[Bukit Jalil Sports School|SSBJ 'A']] has competed in the [[Malaysia President Cup]] since 2010. SSBJ is considered to be the national feeder to the [[Harimau Muda B]] Team
